Description:
As you go down the marsh, you find that you reach deep water and cannot progress.

Fortunately there is a boat on the shore but it is broken, it is too late to turn around so your only option is to repair the boat as much as you can and see if it holds.

At first glance, you see some boards around you and some plants that could be used to repair the boat.
DescriptionAction: How will you try to repair it?
